## Key Business Rules

| Rule | Why It Matters |
|------|----------------|
| Offboarding does NOT delete Brand Vault data | Client's brand work is their IP — must be preserved |
| Offboarded clients lose course access | RLS + route guard blocks course steps |
| Re-enrollment restores access immediately | No extra steps needed after re-enroll |
| Admin notes are internal only | Students never see `enrollments.notes` |

